I feel I’ve aged like 84 years since the trailer dropped but somehow it also feels like it’s ending so fast?!!!!!!???? I think I’ll probably cry more when season 3 ends then I did when I found out season 4 of OG was the last (and I cried a decent amount). Okay. Brb, while I go cry (acting like I wasn’t already crying while writing this).

I’m not ready to only get background Elu after this season is over :( I’ll miss Lucas too much.
